data.title: Nancy Carlson To Wed in July
data.text:
Announcement has been made by Mr. and Mrs. D. Bret Carlson of the engagement of their daughter, Nancy Carlson, to Timothy John Berners-Lee, a son of Mr. and Mrs. Conway Berners-Lee of London. A July wedding is planned.

Miss Carlson, a graduate of Brown University, is a programmer-analyst at the World Health Organization in Geneva. Her father retired as a partner in the law firm of Debevoise & Plimpton in New York.

Mr. Berners-Lee, a graduate of Oxford University, is a software engineer at the European Particle Physics Laboratory in Geneva. His father is a retired mathematician.
